{"type":"message","id":"cce74ae0","parentId":"6c984002","timestamp":"2026-04-03T14:03:53.582Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_pYWKTwBflSiX4SuIZViwwoZV|fc_0720dca2e9063a210169cfc8c5d4848191a16adf958e295853","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"FullName                                                                               \r\n--------                                                                               \r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3                        \r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\B2_runtime_control_flow.md\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\architecture.md        \r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\inputs.md              \r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\operators.md           \r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\post_dispatch.md       \r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\runtime_layout.md      \r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md          \r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\workflow_bootstrap.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":436,"aggregated":"FullName                                                                               \r\n--------                                                                               \r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3                        \r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\B2_runtime_control_flow.md\r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\architecture.md        \r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\inputs.md              \r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\operators.md           \r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\post_dispatch.md       \r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\runtime_layout.md      \r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\supervisor.md          \r\nC:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S3\\workflow_bootstrap.md","cwd":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775225033562}}
{"type":"message","id":"0d7d9112","parentId":"cce74ae0","timestamp":"2026-04-03T14:03:59.493Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Feito.\n\nOrganizei em:\n\n```text\n.openclaw/workspace/content_factory_block2/\n```\n\n### Ficou assim\n- `content_factory_block2/B2_runtime_control_flow.md`\n- `content_factory_block2/S3/architecture.md`\n- `content_factory_block2/S3/inputs.md`\n- `content_factory_block2/S3/operators.md`\n- `content_factory_block2/S3/post_dispatch.md`\n- `content_factory_block2/S3/runtime_layout.md`\n- `content_factory_block2/S3/supervisor.md`\n- `content_factory_block2/S3/workflow_bootstrap.md`\n\nAcho que esta escolha foi boa mesmo — deixa espaço para no futuro existir:\n- `content_factory_block2/S4/`\n- `content_factory_block2/S5/`\n- `content_factory_block2/S6/`\n- docs do `b2_director`\n- contracts/schemas do bloco\n\n## Próximo passo natural\nAgora eu iria para:\n### **planeamento do `b2_director`**\ncom:\n- papel exacto\n- missão\n- limites\n- runtime/workspace dele\n- contract de entrada/saída\n- relação com Perseus / Paperclip\n\nSe quiser, já puxo essa peça.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0720dca2e9063a210169cfc8cc0e588191aaf5fcdab0539764\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":416,"output":265,"cacheRead":80384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81065,"cost":{"input":0.0010400000000000001,"output":0.003975,"cacheRead":0.020096,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.025111}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775225033583,"responseId":"resp_0720dca2e9063a210169cfc8cb4da081919deb2360c3e685fe"}}
