{"type":"message","id":"1b68734a","parentId":"1e2592fb","timestamp":"2026-04-03T15:41:10.656Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Feito — criei também a memória de hoje:\n\n- `memory/2026-04-03.md`\n\nAgora o estado ficou guardado em:\n- `CONTEXT.md`\n- `MEMORY.md`\n- `memory/2026-04-03.md`\n- `content_factory_block2/EXECUTION_PLAN.md`\n- `content_factory_block2/EXECUTION_STATE.md`\n\nEntão se fores resetar, a continuidade está bem mais protegida.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0720dca2e9063a210169cfdf963c0c8191b78c0c5a2ffdc4bd\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":206,"output":102,"cacheRead":165888,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":166196,"cost":{"input":0.000515,"output":0.0015300000000000001,"cacheRead":0.041471999999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.04351699999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775230867292,"responseId":"resp_0720dca2e9063a210169cfdf95240081919ff83359dfe1253b"}}
